59:56.893 --> 01:00:00.727
Babe, babe, babe, what happened?
What happened?

01:00:01.764 --> 01:00:04.756
Oh, God. What is this?

01:00:04.968 --> 01:00:05.992
Honey.

01:00:06.936 --> 01:00:09.700
