01:11:42.298 --> 01:11:43.731
Excuse me.

01:11:43.966 --> 01:11:45.297
Sure.

01:12:25.941 --> 01:12:28.705
Come on, your public awaits you.

01:12:31.613 --> 01:12:35.310
