It's hot. Hold on one second.

01:13:01.243 --> 01:13:04.178
Hey, where the hell you been?
Excuse me?

01:13:04.380 --> 01:13:06.041
- Where is it?
- Where's what? My...

01:13:06.281 --> 01:13:09.409
Maya. All right, now you're
as crazy as your boyfriend.

